com.safenetinc.luna.provider.param

Class LunaParametersBIP32

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.security.AlgorithmParametersSpi
      • com.safenetinc.luna.provider.param.LunaParametersBIP32

  • public class LunaParametersBIP32
extends java.security.AlgorithmParametersSpi
    Specifies the parameters necessary for Hierarchical Deterministic KeyPair derivation mechanism. An instance of this class is immutable.

    • Field Summary

      Fields

      protected java.security.Key baseKey

      protected java.lang.String path
      The key derivation path in BIP44 notation.
